# T52.2: editline auto-generated build artifacts.
# These files are produced by the build (chared.c + common.c + emacs.c + vi.c
# + help.c source-of-truth → makelist scripts emit common.h / editline.c /
# emacs.h / fcns.c / fcns.h / help.c / help.h / vi.h). Tracking the generated
# copies caused merge churn and false-bug-noise (regenerated on every clean
# build with timestamp/signature drift). Generated source headers + the np/*.o_a
# object archives are ignored here so the working tree stays clean.

# Generated headers + sources from makelist
common.h
editline.c
emacs.h
fcns.c
fcns.h
help.c
help.h
vi.h

# np/ archive objects from build
np/*.o_a
